message: With YC interviews being about a week away, I was curious about how everyone was feeling and how things were coming with your prep.

I've been mainly meeting with investors (and finishing personal taxes); the former has been quite productive in addition to just money.  Luckily, cofounder has been working on useful technical/product stuff in parallel.  The phone call with Harj was pretty good.

Heads down, no time for feeling.  Maybe I can do that next year ;o)  People are staying tuned for features I'm in the middle of writing.  Work work work...  Currently prep is having a better, more successful and awesome product than we did last night, or the night before.
@workingBen bingo, same here at the moment. Still working on the product at the moment, making sure it's as awesome as possible.
